   php-eval action:
   ----------------
       Run drush php-eval over a drupal installation

       INPUT:
           code:
              Description: The particular code to evaluate.
                   Prompt: PHP code
                     Type: string
                 Optional: false
               Validation: ^/[a-zA-Z\-_\d/]+$
                   Length: 255

           no:
              Description: Assume 'no' as answer to all prompts.
                   Prompt: Assume No
                     Type: boolean
                 Optional: true

           root:
              Description: Drupal root directory to use.
                   Prompt: Root directory
                     Type: string
